personality_trait.name: Imaginative
personality_trait.definition: Able to think symbolically and play with ideas.

personality_trait.name: Observant
personality_trait.definition: keenly perceptive and aware of one's environment

personality_trait.name: Particular
personality_trait.definition: has preferences that are exact and detailed

personality_trait.name: Superficial
personality_trait.definition: likes to stay on the surface and not dig too deeply

personality_trait.name: Visionary
personality_trait.definition: can imagine how actions and ideas pursued in the present will effect the future

personality_trait.name: Eclectic
personality_trait.definition: Having a variety of blended interests, tastes, beliefs, style

personality_trait.name: Concrete
personality_trait.definition: A style of thinking that values facts and real objects

personality_trait.name: Focused
personality_trait.definition: can concentrate one's mind, either because of a sense of drivenness, or as a result of interest or self-discipline

personality_trait.name: Open-Minded
personality_trait.definition: Having a mind receptive to new ideas or ideas contrary to one's own beliefs

personality_trait.name: Realistic
personality_trait.definition: has a real sense of what is practical and workable
